{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_79","type":"agent_message","text":"The JVM-agent route is blocked a second way: this test project pins its `Test` launcher to Java 21, so Gradle is starting the instrumented JVM on a JDK 21 toolchain, and the native-image agent from the required GraalVM 25 refuses to attach. I’m checking whether the test harness already has a supported override for the launcher version before I consider any repo changes to make the agent path usable under the mandated GraalVM."}}
